Package entity

Class Log

java.lang.Object
entity.Log
public class Log
extends java.lang.Object
The Log class represents a log entity, the log entity is used to store log files of the admin app
Author:
JIAYING

  • Field Summary

    Fields 
    Modifier and Type Field Description
    java.lang.String datetime
    This string is used for the log object to store the date and time of log occurrence
    java.lang.String description
    This string is used for the log object to store the description of what happen
    int loglvl
    This int is used for the log object to store the loglvl, the loglvl is used to store the level severity
    java.lang.String username
    This string is used for the log object to know who created the log entry
